title: Bask in luxury at Park Place Northville. The finest in upscale living.
posting_body: ['Welcome to Park Place Northville!', '43001 Northville Place Dr Northville, MI 48167', 'Rental Size:', '2 BR - 2 BA - 1041 sq ft |', 'Per Month:', '$1680 - $2015 |', 'Lease Length:', '4-Month, 5-Month, 6-Month, 7-Month, 8-Month, 9-Month, 10-Month, 11-Month, 12-Month, 13-Month, 14-Month', 'show contact info', 'YES, WE ARE OPEN!', 'CALL NOW TO SCHEDULE AN IN-PERSON TOUR!', 'OR LET US SHOW YOU THROUGH FACETIME!', 'Start your new chapter at Park Place!', 'Our luxury apartments for rent in Northville have everything you need!', 'From spacious floor plans to high-end amenities that are sure to help you live in style and luxury!', 'Click through our photo gallery and see why you should call Park Place your new home in Northville, Michigan!', 'Our community features:', '◾ 24 Hour Fitness Gym', '◾ Business Center', '◾ Clubhouse', '◾ Laundry Facilities', '◾ Online Payments Available', '◾ Sundeck', '◾ Swimming Pool', '◾ Tennis Court', '◾ Volleyball Court', '◾ Wifi-Cafe', '◾ Center Sidewalks Throughout', '◾ Close to Downtown Northville', '◾ Concierge', '◾ House Plant Watering Service', '◾ Lush Landscaping', '◾ Luxury Building', '◾ Minutes from shopping, dining, and entertainment', '◾ Package Receiving', '◾ Pets Allowed', '◾ Smoke-Free', 'Our unit features:', '◾ Built-in Microwave', '◾ Central Air', '◾ Deluxe and Premium Available (Select Units)', '◾ Frost Free Refrigerator', '◾ Heating', '◾ Large Picture Windows', '◾ Private Entrances (Select Units)', '◾ Range', '◾ Spacious Master Bedroom', '◾ Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Contact us for more information!', '--', 'show contact info', '--', 'Our Pet-Policy:', 'We are extremely pet-friendly, however, dogs are only allowed in Buildings 1 through 10!', 'Also, we even have "While Away" pet care!', 'Pet rent is $30 per pet.', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Property Management:', 'JRK Property Holdings', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', 'D20AF8A1DD5F4A3']
